abstract: Partisan news sites that were clever with social media had a strong effect on the presidential campaign. What does that mean for the news business?
snippet: Partisan news sites that were clever with social media had a strong effect on the presidential campaign. What does that mean for the news business?
lead_paragraph: A fine 1997 documentary about obsession has a title well suited to the media landscape in this election year: “Fast, Cheap and Out of Control.”

headline.main: Daily Report: Online Media That Helped Make Trump
